metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Young Turks is more basic than the typical song, having below average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Young Turks has sections analyzed in the following keys: B♭ Mixolydian,  and E♭ Major.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: Changed to B-flat Mixolydian because the rest of the song is E-flat major (Eb major and Bb mix use the same scale).
